1197
01:50:00,072 --> 01:50:00,905
Jawab!

1198
01:50:01,947 --> 01:50:03,614
Qingming!

1199
01:50:03,697 --> 01:50:05,739
Jika aku menjadi roh pelindungmu,

1200
01:50:05,822 --> 01:50:08,822
kau akan mewarisi semua
karma burukku,

1201
01:50:08,905 --> 01:50:10,447
kehilangan segala emosi,

1202
01:50:10,530 --> 01:50:13,864
dan selamanya menjadi
musuh umat manusia.

1203
01:50:18,114 --> 01:50:19,197
Aku bertanya padamu,

1204
01:50:19,697 --> 01:50:21,197
apa kau mau patuh?

1205
01:50:35,697 --> 01:50:37,739
Aku, Xiangliu,

1206
01:50:37,822 --> 01:50:42,239
akan menjadi roh pelindung Qingming
mulai dari saat ini.

1207
01:50:42,780 --> 01:50:44,989
Sehidup semati,

1208
01:50:45,072 --> 01:50:48,155
tak akan berkhianat.

1209
01:51:20,947 --> 01:51:22,155
Semua mantra roh pelindung

1210
01:51:23,697 --> 01:51:24,989
sudah dicabut.

1211
01:51:26,655 --> 01:51:28,655
Master!

1212
01:51:30,697 --> 01:51:33,572
<i>Mulai kini, kita tak saling terhubung.</i>

1213
01:52:41,655 --> 01:52:43,447
<i>Pada bulan ke-7 tahun Gengxu,</i>

1214
01:52:43,530 --> 01:52:45,364
<i>bencana mengubah Kota Pingjing.</i>

1215
01:52:45,447 --> 01:52:47,947
<i>Badai timbul, topan datang.</i>

1216
01:52:49,072 --> 01:52:51,030
<i>Itu adalah catatan resmi para sejarawan.</i>

1217
01:52:51,822 --> 01:52:53,447
<i>Kebenarannya berbeda</i>

1218
01:52:53,530 --> 01:52:54,780
<i>dengan laporanku.</i>

1219
01:52:55,614 --> 01:52:56,864
<i>Pertempuran Jembatan Roh</i>

1220
01:52:57,364 --> 01:52:58,864
<i>menentukan takdir dunia.</i>

1221
01:52:59,447 --> 01:53:02,155
<i>Qingming dan para roh pelindungnya
bertaruh nyawa,</i>

1222
01:53:02,822 --> 01:53:04,989
<i>tapi entah kenapa aku</i>

1223
01:53:05,072 --> 01:53:06,572
<i>yang dianggap pahlawan besar.</i>

1224
01:53:07,989 --> 01:53:08,822
<i>Qingming,</i>

1225
01:53:10,030 --> 01:53:11,614
<i>apa yang sebenarnya kau alami?</i>

1226
01:53:12,614 --> 01:53:13,697
<i>Aku tak begitu paham.</i>

1227
01:53:15,614 --> 01:53:19,072
<i>Tapi melihat ketegasanmu memutus ikatan
dengan para roh pelindungmu,</i>

1228
01:53:20,030 --> 01:53:21,864
<i>pasti bukan itu yang kau kehendaki.</i>

1229
01:53:28,072 --> 01:53:29,030
<i>Pengorbananmu</i>

1230
01:53:29,614 --> 01:53:31,155
<i>membawa kedamaian,</i>

1231
01:53:32,155 --> 01:53:34,239
<i>tapi para roh pelindung
tersebar entah ke mana.</i>

1232
01:53:35,280 --> 01:53:38,572
<i>Aku juga tak lagi
punya tempat untuk pulang.</i>

1233
01:54:10,614 --> 01:54:11,822
<i>Qingming.</i>

1234
01:54:12,405 --> 01:54:14,989
<i>Tak peduli siapa master
atau roh pelindung,</i>

1235
01:54:16,155 --> 01:54:18,322
<i>kami semua menantikan kepulanganmu.</i>

1236
01:54:18,822 --> 01:54:20,822
<i>Kami bersedia berbagi beban denganmu.</i>

1237
01:54:24,280 --> 01:54:26,114
<i>Bukankah arti dari mantra roh pelindung</i>

1238
01:54:26,197 --> 01:54:28,239
<i>adalah berbagi suka duka</i>

1239
01:54:28,739 --> 01:54:31,530
<i>sampai ajal menjelang,
dan selamanya tak akan berkhianat?</i>

